  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ゼロスのファッションセンスはゼロッス！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Zelos' fashion sense is zero!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Same situation as Kyle's.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>はぁ？
突然なに言ってくれてんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? What the heck are you talking about,
all of a sudden?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>会話センスもゼロッス！
恋愛技術もゼロッス！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Zero conversation skills!
Zero romantic charisma!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ほう。
俺さまを百戦錬磨の
ハニーハンターと知っての台詞か？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really now?
Do you speak such dialogue knowing I
happen to be a veteran Honey Hunter?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんだこいつ、おもしろいなー</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who is this guy? He's pretty funny!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おもしろくない！
いくぜ、ロイドくん！
売られたケンカは買ってやらなきゃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He is NOT funny!
Let's go, Lloyd-kun!
When given a battle proposition,
you have to accept it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱりこうなるのか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I knew it was gonna end up like this...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
